            "Cappadocia fairy chimneys, Vardzia cave monastery, Kazbegi mountains, Lake Sevan, Armenian Apostolic churches",
            "~€1800–2400 per person (incl. flights, hotels & dining)",
            new[]{
                ("Istanbul & Cappadocia, Turkey","4 days","Hagia Sophia, Grand Bazaar, then fly to Cappadocia — hot air balloon over fairy chimneys at sunrise, underground cities of Derinkuyu.", "Book the hot air balloon at least 1 week ahead — it sells out fast and weather cancellations are common."),
